System.register("chunks:///_virtual/en.ts",["cc"],(function(e){var t;return{setters:[function(e){t=e.cclegacy}],execute:function(){t._RF.push({},"ca27e02wFJKnJ4i8XuwXQbX","en",void 0);var a=window,n=e("languages",{dialog:{game1_1:"Hoss, the miniature horse has gotten a bit plump lately. It's much less active.",game1_2:"It often stays in its stable and hardly moves. It even finishes its feed very fast.",game1_3:"Hmm, maybe it's not getting enough exercise.",game1_4:"Partner, help me watch its activity and encourage it to exercise more so it can get healthy again!",game2_1:"Hoss, we need to move the wolf, raccoon, and feed to the temperate zone today, but they can't be together!",game2_2:"The wolf will chase the raccoon, and the raccoon will eat the feed. It's too dangerous like this.",game2_3:"Understood. We'll have to transport them in batches.",game2_4:"Partner, help me plan each trip. Ensure safety—and don't overload the donkey.",game3_1:"Hoss, there's a problem with the conservation database!",game3_2:"The IUCN categories for the Przewalski's horse, African wild ass, and zebra are all mixed up. Patrol resources got distributed incorrectly.",game3_3:"That won't do! Wrong categories will affect the entire conservation project.",game3_4:"Partner, help me restore the correct conservation order so the resources can go back to the species that need them the most!",game4_1:"－－！－－！",game4_2:"Hoss, bad news! Monitoring of the prairie shows strangers have intruded the rhino area. We also found cut fence and tire tracks!",game4_3:"Those are signs of poachers. We have to act immediately!",game4_4:"Partner, help me patrol every area. Drive out anyone suspicious and protect the rhinos!",game5_1:"Hoss, we have a situation! A young zebra got separated during migrating, and now another zebra claims to be its mother.",game5_2:"But the little zebra remembers its mother's stripes looked different...",game5_3:"Stripes are nature's password.",game5_4:"Partner, compare the stripes quickly! Find the differences within 30 seconds so we can expose the impostor!",game6_1:"Hoss, the water level at the oasis keeps dropping! Someone believes an animal is stealing water. I've marked all the hoofprints on-site.",game6_2:"Don't jump to conclusions. The truth is in the details.",game6_3:"Partner, help me compare the hoofprints to find the real 'suspect'!",game7_1:"Hoss, we found a Malayan tapir fallen by the forest path during night patrol. It looks weak from hunger!",game7_2:"It may not have found suitable food. Partner, we need to help it recover energy!",game7_3:"Help the tapir choose the right food. Once it regains strength, it can keep spreading seeds in the rainforest!"},gameplay:{1:'⏱ Time limit: 30 seconds!\nKeep shaking your phone to make the miniature horse run forward like "clippety-clop".\n\nThe faster you shake → the faster the miniature horse runs → the quicker the weight-loss bar cleat!\n\n⚠️ Clear Conditions\nEmpty the progress bar before the time runs out to clear the stage!\n\n⚠️ Reminder: For the best experience, use the Safari/Chrome. Hold your phone tight and avoid shaking too hard. Safety first!',2:'You are a "cargo dispatcher"! Use the donkey to transport the wolf, raccoon, and feed in batches.\n\nRules:The donkey can carry one item at a time (wolf, raccoon, feed).\nWolf + raccoon cannot stay alone together → the raccoon gets bullied.\nRaccoon + feed cannot stay alone → the feed gets eaten.\nPlan wisely to deliver everything safely.\n\n⚠️ Clear Conditions\nNo time or attempt limit. Transport all three items safely to clear the stage.',3:"You are a \"conservation password assistant\"! Help Detective Hoss restore the correct IUCN categories order.\n\nThree species appear (Przewalski's horse, African wild ass, Chapman's zebra), but the order is incorrect.\nEnter one guess per turn by selecting the IUCN categories.\nHints appear each turn:\n\n(A) number correct and in correct position\n(B) number correct but in wrong position\n\n⚠️ Clear Conditions\nNo time or attempt limit. Correctly restore all three species’ IUCN orders to clear the stage.",4:'You are a "temporary ranger".Help Detective Hoss chase away poachers sneaking into the prairie.\n\nPoacher silhouettes appear randomly—tap them fast!\nReact too slowly, poachers will increase, putting rhinos in danger.\nStay focus and keep tapping until time runs out.\n\n⚠️ Clear Conditions\nChase away 30 poachers within the time limit to clear the stage.',5:'You are a "stripe identifier"!Help Detective Hoss expose the fake mother.\nCompare the "picture of mother" and the "real-or-fake mother" on the scene.\n\nTap to find 5 differences within 30 seconds.\n\nFind all the differences to uncover the swindler.\n\n⚠️ Clear Conditions\nFind 5 differences in time limit so the little zebra can reunite with its real mother.',6:'You are a "hoofprint surveyor"! Help Detective Hoss find the truth behind the oasis water drop.\n\n12 facedown cards show different hoofprints(African wild ass, donkey, zebra, human, etc.).\n\nFlip and compare the only match pair within 30 seconds.\nReveal the "culprit" and debunk the rumors.\n\n⚠️ Clear Conditions\nFind the matching hoofprint pair within the time limit to complete the mission.',7:'You are a member of a "food rescue team"! Help Detective Hoss save the starving Malayan tapir.\nFood falls from above—catch only the safe ones:\n\nbananas, papayas, yam leaves: +10 points\n\nbombs: -20 points\nMove the Malayan tapir left and right to catch food and avoid danger.\n\n⚠️ Clear Conditions\nScore 200 points within the time limit so the Malayan tapir can recover its strength to clear the stage.'},ui:{1:"{0} second(s) left",2:"Select item to begin delivery",3:"Delivering...",4:"Transport {0} on donkey",5:"Unload {0} from donkey",6:"{0}: Not on same side.",7:"Wolf",8:"Raccoon",9:"Feed",10:"3 selections completed.",11:"Please select 3 items.",12:"Hurry! Tap the poachers to chase away!",13:"Find 5 differences in the picture below",14:"Picture of real-or-fake mother",15:"Picture held by Hoss",16:"Points",17:"Arrived"}});a.languages||(a.languages={}),a.languages.en=n,t._RF.pop()}}}));

System.register("chunks:///_virtual/resources",["./en.ts","./zh.ts"],(function(){return{setters:[null,null],execute:function(){}}}));

System.register("chunks:///_virtual/zh.ts",["cc"],(function(n){var a;return{setters:[function(n){a=n.cclegacy}],execute:function(){a._RF.push({},"6434bWJGNFIcYty9BdwFj+d","zh",void 0);var e=window,g=n("languages",{dialog:{game1_1:"霍斯，最近迷你馬的體態有點圓，活動量明顯下降。",game1_2:"牠常待在馬棚裡不太走動，連飼料都吃得特別快。",game1_3:"嗯，這可能是運動不足造成的。",game1_4:"小助手幫我觀察牠的活動狀況，協助牠多運動，恢復健康吧！",game2_1:"霍斯，今天要把灰狼、小浣熊和飼料運到溫帶區，但牠們不能同時放在一起！",game2_2:"狼會追小浣熊，小浣熊又會偷吃飼料，這樣太危險了。",game2_3:"了解，這得靠分批運送。小助手，",game2_4:"幫我規劃每次要載誰，確保安全、也別讓驢子超載。",game3_1:"霍斯，保育資料庫出問題了！",game3_2:"蒙古野馬、非洲野驢和斑馬的 IUCN 等級全被弄亂，巡護資源分配錯了。",game3_3:"這可不行！錯誤的等級會影響整個保育計畫。",game3_4:"小助手，快協助我還原正確的保育順序，讓資源回到最需要的物種手中！",game4_1:"－－！－－！",game4_2:"霍斯，不好了！草原監控顯示有陌生人闖入犀牛區，現場還發現剪斷的圍網和車輪痕跡！",game4_3:"這是盜獵的徵兆，必須立刻行動！",game4_4:"小助手，快協助我巡查各區，驅離可疑人員，確保犀牛安全！",game5_1:"霍斯，有狀況！小斑馬在遷徙途中和族群走散，現在有一匹斑馬說自己是牠的媽媽。",game5_2:"但小斑馬記得，媽媽的條紋好像不太一樣……",game5_3:"條紋是大自然的密碼。",game5_4:"小助手，快幫忙比對！三十秒內找出不同，才能揭穿冒牌貨！",game6_1:"霍斯，綠洲的水位連續下降！有人懷疑有動物在偷水，我已經標記了現場的足跡。",game6_2:"別急著下結論，真相藏在細節裡。",game6_3:"小助手，快來幫我比對足跡，找出真正的『嫌疑犯』吧！",game7_1:"霍斯，夜間巡查時發現一隻馬來貘倒在林徑旁，看起來是因為太餓而虛弱了！",game7_2:"牠可能找不到合適的食物。小助手，我們得幫牠補充能量！",game7_3:"協助牠挑對食物，恢復體力後，就能繼續替雨林播種！"},gameplay:{1:"⏱限時 30 秒！\n不斷搖晃手機，迷你馬 就會「噠噠噠」往前奔跑。\n\n搖得越快 → 迷你馬跑得越快 → 瘦身進度條清得更快！\n\n⚠️ 通關條件\n在時間結束前清空進度條，就能成功過關！\n\n⚠️ 小提醒：建議使用「Safari / Chrome」瀏覽器遊玩，可達最佳體驗效果，並握緊手機，避免激烈甩動，安全第一！",2:"化身「載運調度員」！操作馴化驢分批運送灰狼、小浣熊與飼料。\n\n規則如下：\n馴化驢一次只能運送一件貨物（灰狼、小浣熊或飼料）。\n灰狼與小浣熊不可單獨留下，否則小浣熊會受欺負。\n小浣熊與飼料不可單獨留下，否則飼料會被偷吃。\n透過合理規劃，確保所有貨物安全抵達目的地。\n\n⚠️ 通關條件\n無時間與次數限制，順利完成三項貨物安全轉運，即可過關。",3:"化身「保育密碼助手」！協助霍斯探長還原正確的 IUCN 等級排序。\n\n三種動物（蒙古野馬、非洲野驢、查普曼斑馬）的等級標籤，但順序被錯置。\n玩家每回合可輸入一組輸入IUCN保育等級。\n\n即時提示：幾項答案與位置正確（Ａ）、幾項答案正確位置錯誤（Ｂ）。\n\n⚠️ 通關條件\n無時間與次數限制，成功還原三種動物的正確 IUCN 等級排序，即完成任務。",4:"化身「臨時巡護員」！協助霍斯探長驅離潛入草原的盜獵團伙。\n\n螢幕上隨機出現偷獵者剪影－快點他們！\n若反應不及，偷獵者會持續增加，白犀牛將陷入危險。\n需保持專注與速度，直到計時結束。\n\n⚠️ 通關條件\n在限定時間內成功驅離30位盜獵者，即可過關。",5:"化身「條紋鑑識員」！協助霍斯探長破解冒牌媽媽事件。\n螢幕上下並列：「媽媽照片」與現場的「真假媽媽」\n\n在 30 秒內點擊畫面，找出的 5 處差異。\n\n成功比對出所有差異，即能揭穿冒牌貨。\n\n⚠️ 通關條件\n於時限內正確找出5處條紋差異，協助小斑馬認回真正的母親。",6:"化身「足跡調查員」！協助霍斯探長釐清綠洲水位下降的真相。\n\n螢幕上隨機排列 12 張覆面牌，內容包含不同足跡（非洲野驢、家驢、斑馬、人類等）。\n\n在 30 秒內翻牌比對，找出唯一一對相同的足跡。\n找出正確足跡，即可揭露「兇手」並破解謠言。\n\n⚠️ 通關條件\n於時限內找出那對完全相同的足跡牌，即判定任務完成。",7:"化身「外勤搜食小組」的一員！協助霍斯探長救援因飢餓倒地的馬來貘。\n\n遊戲螢幕會不斷掉落不同物件，包括可食物（香蕉、木瓜與地瓜藤加10分）與不可食物（炸彈扣20分）。\n\n操控馬來貘左右移動，在限時內接取正確食物並避開錯誤物。\n\n⚠️ 通關條件\n於時限內累積200分數，讓馬來貘恢復體力，即可過關。"},ui:{1:"剩餘{0}秒",2:"請選擇貨物開始運輸",3:"運輸中...",4:"搬運 {0} 上驢",5:"放下 {0}",6:"{0} 不在同一岸上",7:"灰狼",8:"小浣熊",9:"飼料",10:"已選滿 3 個",11:"請先選滿 3 個",12:"快點擊盜獵者進行驅趕！",13:"找出下方照片 5 處不同處",14:"現場真假媽媽圖片",15:"霍斯手上的照片",16:"分",17:"已抵達"}});e.languages||(e.languages={}),e.languages.zh=g,a._RF.pop()}}}));

